  "texts": [
    "Given the disproportionate impact of LLMs on maintenance activities and established projects with rich context, firms should consider strategies to incentivize contributions to early-stage projects and capability innovation.",
    "This might include mentorship programs, dedicated time allocations for exploratory work, or specific recognition for big-picture contributions.",
    "Our current findings have certain limitations common across all research related to innovation.",
    "Our study focuses on a specific time window (October 2021 to December 2022) when GitHub Copilot was the primary decent-quality code completion LLM available, creating a rare natural experiment opportunity that is now quite hard to replicate.",
    "This temporal boundary was necessary to maintain a clean natural experiment that isolates LLM's impact before ChatGPT's introduction changed the landscape and eliminated the possibility of \"clean\" control groups in field settings."
  ],
